Class JingleIQPacket

java.lang.Object
  org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.Packet
      org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.IQ
          com.cornell.opencomm.jingleimpl.JingleIQPacket

public class JingleIQPacket
extends org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.IQ

This class models a Jingle Element as defined by XEP-0166 This class is based on the earlier Jingle code being used by the network team and is an attempt to make it more general.

Author:
Abhishek, Ming
